        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1978-02-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1978-02-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="480"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d480">
                <head>480. Note From President <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> to
                    Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_VCR_1">Vance</persName> and the
                    President’s Assistant for National Security Affairs (<persName corresp="#p_BZ_1"
                        >Brzezinski</persName>)<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d480fn1">Source:
                        Department of State, Executive Secretariat Files, Lot 84D161, Box 1,
                        Miscellaneous. No classification marking. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                            >Carter</persName> hand-wrote the note. <persName corresp="#p_BZ_1"
                            >Brzezinski</persName> forwarded the note under cover of a February 27
                        memorandum. (Ibid.)</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1978-02-27">February 27, 1978</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Cy &amp; Zbig</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>We need to evolve soon <gloss target="#t_US_1">US</gloss> position re <gloss
                        target="#t_UN_1">UN</gloss> Disarmament Conference. We’re in danger of being
                    clobbered by all nations for arms sales &amp; by Soviets on <gloss
                        target="#t_ER_1">ER</gloss> weapons.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="strong">J.C.</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
